form.text: We are not enemies but friends. We must not be enemies. Though passion may have strained it must not break our bonds of affection. The mystic cords of memory shall swell when again touched, as surely they will be, by the better angels of nature.

설명하지마라. 친구라면 설명할
필요가 없고, 적이라면 어차피
당신을 믿으려 하지 않을테니까.

Never explain--your friends do not need it
and your enemies will not believe you anyway.
